prompts.frontCover:
Comic book style illustration of a romantic anniversary beach scene at sunset, featuring Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo as the main characters. The scene is dynamic, with a slightly low angle perspective looking up at the couple.

Lao Lao is sitting on a cozy, patterned beach blanket, leaning back against Jordan with a happy, relaxed expression. Jordan is sitting behind her, with his arms wrapped gently around her in a warm hug. They are both looking at each other lovingly. Lao Lao wears a light blue crewneck sweatshirt and Jordan wears a comfortable tan hoodie, similar to the photo.

They are sipping from unique custom drinks: boba tea served in hollowed-out coconut shells, complete with large boba straws. The sunset is dramatic and vibrant, filling the sky with fiery oranges, deep purples, and brilliant pinks, with dynamic action lines streaking from the setting sun to emphasize the moment. The ocean has gentle waves with white caps, and a couple of silhouetted palm trees are visible in the background. The art style uses bold black outlines, halftone dot patterns for shading, and a saturated, high-contrast color palette to capture a classic comic book feel.

In the clear sky area in the center of the card, the text "Happy Anniversary, My Love" is written in a beautiful, flowing, white cursive script.
